Package edu.cuny.jfree.data.category

Interface Summary
ListCategoryDataset A category dataset that manages a collection of lists of objects in a 2-dimensional categorized space, instead of a collection of single values in such a space in regular CategoryDataset.
 

Class Summary
AbstractListCategoryDataset An abstract implementation of ListCategoryDataset using org.jfree.data.KeyedObjects2D.
DefaultIntervalListCategoryDataset extends AbstractListCategoryDataset to manipulate list of Intervals.
DefaultValueListCategoryDataset extends AbstractListCategoryDataset to manipulate list of values.
